<paragraph id="E0059FBE6878236F936A1A74DC99F8F5" pageId="0" pageNumber="47">Central African Republic, Dzanga-Sangha Special Reserve, Camp 5, 15-16.II.2005, P. Annoyer (♂ holotypus); Dzanga-Sangha Special Reserve, Camp 5, 7-8.II.2005 (light), P. Annoyer (1♀); Dzanga-Sangha Special Reserve, 15-16.X.2008 (light), P. Annoyer (1♀) (BMPC).</paragraph>
